OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FNato chief Mark Rutte highlighted the
OL,8,Fefforts being led by Sir Keir Starmer
OL,9,Fto secure the vital Strait of Hormuz
OL,10,Fshipping lane during a "frank and open
OL,11,Fdiscussion" with Donald Trump.
OL,13,FThe diplomat pointed to the "positive"
OL,14,Faction being taken by the Prime
OL,15,FMinister during a meeting in
OL,16,FWashington, where he acknowledged the
OL,17,FUS president was "clearly
OL,18,Fdisappointed" with the response of the
OL,19,Fmilitary alliance to the Iran war.
OL,26,@rD@XOUsD@KO]uD@]OUuD@fO]yD@ROUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
