OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FIn an interview with CNN after the
OL,8,FWhite House talks, Mr Rutte said he
OL,9,Fhad pointed out the "large majority of
OL,10,FEuropean nations" had been helpful to
OL,11,FAmerica during the conflict and lived
OL,12,Fup to their commitments.
OL,14,FBut he had failed to calm Mr Trump's
OL,15,Fannoyance as the president later
OL,16,Fposted on his Truth Social platform:
OL,17,F"NATO WASN'T THERE WHEN WE NEEDED
OL,18,FTHEM, AND THEY WON'T BE THERE IF WE
OL,19,FNEED THEM AGAIN."
OL,26,@qD@UOUrD@QO]yD@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FOnly earlier, the White House said
OL,8,FBritain and other Nato allies had
OL,9,F"turned their backs" on the American
OL,10,Fpeople during the war.
OL,12,FMr Trump also argued the long-standing
OL,13,Fsecurity organisation had been "tested
OL,14,Fand they failed".
OL,16,FHe has previously raised the
OL,17,Fpossibility of the US quitting Nato,
OL,18,Fbranding it a "paper tiger".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@TO]uD@`OUvD@PO]zD@OOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FThe refusal by the UK to be drawn into
OL,8,Fthe offensive against Iran, dubbed
OL,9,FOperation Epic Fury by the US, and to
OL,10,Frestrict the use of its bases by
OL,11,FAmerican forces has put a severe
OL,12,Fstrain on relations between Sir Keir
OL,13,FStarmer and Mr Trump.
OL,15,FThe US president has also previously
OL,16,Fcomplained about the contributions
OL,17,Fpaid in by fellow Nato members,
OL,18,Farguing America has been carrying
OL,19,Fother countries financially.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FAhead of the US-Iran ceasefire being
OL,8,Fannounced, the UK had chaired a
OL,9,Fmeeting of military planners from a
OL,10,Fcoalition of nations examining long-
OL,11,Fterm measures to secure the strait,
OL,12,Fwhich had been all but closed off by
OL,13,FTehran during the conflict, causing a
OL,14,Fshock to global trade.
OL,16,FMilitary representatives from over 30
OL,17,Fnations joined the virtual conference
OL,18,Fto explore ways to make the shipping
OL,19,Froute safe and accessible once
OL,20,Fhostilities have ended.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FFollowing the truce, a joint statement
OL,8,Fby world leaders, including Sir Keir,
OL,9,Fsaid they would "contribute to
OL,10,Fensuring freedom of navigation in the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz".
OL,13,FBut White House press secretary
OL,14,FKaroline Leavitt was dismissive of the
OL,15,Foffer when asked at a news conference.
OL,17,FSharing a quote from Mr Trump on Nato
OL,18,Fin response, she said: "They were
OL,19,Ftested and they failed."
OL,26,@qD@QOUsD@QO]zD@XOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FShe added: "It's quite sad that Nato
OL,8,Fturned their backs on the American
OL,9,Fpeople over the course of the last six
OL,10,Fweeks, when it's the American people
OL,11,Fwho have been funding their defence."
OL,13,FSpeaking to CNN, Mr Rutte said: "Let
OL,14,Fme be absolutely clear, he (Mr Trump)
OL,15,Fis clearly disappointed and with many
OL,16,FNato allies, and I can see his point.
OL,26,@oD@LOUsD@eO]uD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,F"But at the same time, I was also able
OL,8,Fto point him to the fact that the
OL,9,Flarge majority of European nations
OL,10,Fhave been helpful with basing, with
OL,11,Flogistics, with overflights, with
OL,12,Fmaking sure that they lived up to
OL,13,F(their) commitments."
OL,15,FHe also said "let's not forget" steps
OL,16,Fbeing taken by the British Prime
OL,17,FMinister aimed at ensuring the future
OL,18,Ffree-flow of trade through the Strait
OL,19,Fof Hormuz.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@UO]wD@NOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FMr Rutte added: "So I also pointed him
OL,8,Fto the positive. But clearly this was
OL,9,Fa very frank, very open discussion,
OL,10,Fbut also discussion between two good
OL,11,Ffriends."
OL,13,FHe went on: "There is a
OL,14,Fdisappointment, clearly, but at the
OL,15,Fsame time, he was also listening
OL,16,Fcarefully to my arguments of what's
OL,17,Fhappening."
OL,26,@oD@QOUsD@IO]uD@MOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FStressing that most European countries
OL,8,Fhad fulfilled their commitments "in a
OL,9,Fcase like this", Mr Rutte said:
OL,10,F"Europe as a platform of power
OL,11,Fprojection for the United States was
OL,12,Fin full play over the last six weeks.
OL,14,F"Yes, it is true, not all European
OL,15,Fnations lived up to those commitments,
OL,16,Fand I totally understand that He is
OL,17,Fdisappointed (about that)."
OL,26,@pD@aOUqD@OO]rD@AOUvD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775703865
OL,3,CNato boss fails to quell Trump's anger
OL,4,Cafter 'frank and open' White House
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FEarlier, Mr Rutte met with US
OL,8,Fsecretary of state Marco Rubio where
OL,9,Fthe pair discussed "burden shifting"
OL,10,Fwithin the alliance.
OL,12,FFollowing the talks, US State
OL,13,FDepartment principal deputy spokesman
OL,14,FTommy Pigott said: "The two leaders
OL,15,Fdiscussed Operation Epic Fury, ongoing
OL,16,FUS-led efforts to bring a negotiated
OL,17,Fend to the Russia-Ukraine war, and
OL,18,Fincreasing co-ordination and burden
OL,19,Fshifting with Nato allies."
OL,26,@qD@TOUqD@dO]vD@TOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
